lformed Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"6654401b-40ef-39cb-a380-96b1c85db25e","name":"Note: Required Fields Present?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Abort — Malformed Input\n\nFails fast with a clear message; triggers the error workflow instead of processing bad data.","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,1030],"id":"8ddbdc5b-f1b7-b088-41f5-4bf5e63708b8","name":"Note: Abort — Malformed Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Frame the Assignment\n\nShapes the item: writes `assignment`, `deadline`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Coordinator Agent","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"80bb5e6e-08e7-fd23-0ce3-04151ed11422","name":"Note: Frame the Assignment"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Coordinator Agent\n\nThe AI brain: reads the input, decides which attached tools to call (and in what order), then composes the answer.\n\nPorts: ①→ Unpack Sections · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"73de4c70-c971-df02-cb89-2937f6bad0d6","name":"Note: Coordinator Agent"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Google Gemini Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `models/gemini-2.5-flash`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 Google AI API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,1090],"id":"f8c397af-a4df-9e50-72b9-8f6c3fc8e435","name":"Note: Google Gemini Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Research Specialist (Sub-workflow)\n\nSpecialist sub-workflow exposed as a callable tool — one narrow capability per tool.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[804,1510],"id":"984ce951-8feb-ae4c-fb59-aed3c75824cb","name":"Note: Research Specialist (Sub-workflow)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Draft Specialist (Sub-workflow)\n\nSpecialist sub-workflow exposed as a callable tool — one narrow capability per tool.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1060,1750],"id":"df450c96-0be1-d047-4c98-3ec107e763a7","name":"Note: Draft Specialist (Sub-workflow)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Review Specialist (Sub-workflow)\n\nSpecialist sub-workflow exposed as a callable tool — one narrow capability per tool.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1492,1510],"id":"5b98d194-85d0-b9ff-e657-4f298fd4555b","name":"Note: Review Specialist (Sub-workflow)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enforce Result Schema\n\nForces the agent's answer into the JSON schema below — downstream nodes rely on this exact shape.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `outputParser`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1654,1090],"id":"ae0aa545-2ca6-f239-cb97-7fa7dc57e35d","name":"Note: Enforce Result Schema"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Unpack Sections\n\nExplodes the `output.sections` array into one item per element.\n\nNext: Persist Deliverable to Airtable","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1978,520],"id":"8ed5432f-3ccb-e904-343d-6ffa3364956d","name":"Note: Unpack Sections"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Deliverable to Airtable\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Load Previous Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2302,520],"id":"2266a46c-595d-2432-c3f8-a9619c8c8faf","name":"Note: Persist Deliverable to Airtable"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Load Previous Snapshot\n\ngoogleSheets — `read` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Compute Drift vs Snapshot · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2626,520],"id":"47e161df-0ba4-67b6-8bf0-29709772e8b2","name":"Note: Load Previous Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Drift vs Snapshot\n\nCustom JavaScript: Compare current metrics with the previous snapshot\n\nNext: Serialize Run Output (CSV)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2950,520],"id":"c9c17bd6-b570-0160-eccf-2df4e681701d","name":"Note: Compute Drift vs Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Serialize Run Output (CSV)\n\nSerializes items to a CSV binary file.\n\nNext: Archive Row Snapshot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3274,520],"id":"468ad2c2-7e1e-8b10-a1dd-1b29ae840bbb","name":"Note: Serialize Run Output (CSV)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Row Snapshot\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Enrich with Reference Data · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3598,520],"id":"66d6e996-eb7f-788f-45a8-8c35c1773261","name":"Note: Archive Row Snapshot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enrich with Reference Data\n\nGET https://enrichment.example.com/v2/lookup — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Fold In Enrichment Fields · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3922,520],"id":"d249197a-cb56-65f7-105b-3bb445ccf852","name":"Note: Enrich with Reference Data"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fold In Enrichment Fields\n\nShapes the item: writes `enrichedAt`, `enrichmentSource`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Stamp Completion Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4246,520],"id":"b6a4b37f-a613-9e95-dbde-9bdc5bbf5164","name":"Note: Fold In Enrichment Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Completion Time\n\nStamps `completedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Persist Run Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4570,520],"id":"a47646a8-9490-06f1-f204-e3c6a27262b9","name":"Note: Stamp Completion Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Run Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Fingerprint for Idempotency","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4894,520],"id":"905e1ac3-ed22-de67-cfa9-d35114c4dd44","name":"Note: Persist Run Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fingerprint for Idempotency\n\nCustom JavaScript: Build a stable idempotency key per draft (djb2 hash, no deps)\n\nNext: Drop Already-Processed Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5218,520],"id":"b80fb200-9667-2e6d-c3da-8f5e62d006da","name":"Note: Fingerprint for Idempotency"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Drop Already-Processed Items\n\nCross-execution dedupe: remembers keys it has processed before and drops repeats — the idempotency guard.\n\nNext: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5542,520],"id":"249d703a-c641-77e3-1c65-dd61c1459069","name":"Note: Drop Already-Processed Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow\n\nDelegates to a reusable sub-workflow (single-responsibility building block) and waits for its result.\n\nPorts: ①→ Record Sub-workflow Result · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5866,520],"id":"1381b09e-34ee-08cb-ae81-ecfaaaea821b","name":"Note: Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Sub-workflow Result\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Sort Drafts Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6190,520],"id":"8afb9099-14ac-45ec-0444-f449816654ad","name":"Note: Record Sub-workflow Result"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Drafts Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6514,520],"id":"b6231538-103b-4b4e-3eca-6df8e2c4239d","name":"Note: Sort Drafts Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[6838,520],"id":"af64d149-00f0-781c-c658-d8d65d786862","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Notion)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7162,520],"id":"45e675f5-6f55-8e87-4bb6-1359e8d13d2b","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Notion)\n\nnotion — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Notion integration token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7486,520],"id":"7f3d3d9b-5aba-2240-9d40-aaf5adef0946","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Notion)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7810,520],"id":"c6b7d64c-e5ce-d54e-da1d-cd800cbe14aa","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7162,1540],"id":"a09a8b41-08bf-4f28-83cc-7d99c6121796","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7486,1540],"id":"e3e05d94-8607-257a-7815-c72f15c23afe","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Park in Dead-Letter Queue\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[7810,1540],"id":"5faf1bb7-6103-8479-2c3e-e91388959601","name":"Note: Park in Dead-Letter Queue"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Draft social posts with Airtable and WordPress and log the results\n\n**Pattern:** Content Generation · **Level:** Architect · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nDraft social posts with Airtable and WordPress and log the results. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual blog posts is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Required Fields Present? → Frame the Assignment → Coordinator Agent → Unpack Sections → Persist Deliverable to Airtable → Load Previous Snapshot → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to content generation without manual effort\n- Anyone automating blog posts in content creation\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Responds in seconds\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Airtable PAT; Google AI API key; Google OAuth2 / service account; Notion integration token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"fecf0b11-7171-793a-9c39-2b5b7ae4dfda","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Failures are also parked in a dead-letter queue for replay. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"dc43ea6d-17cc-5316-e026-bbe309b0786b","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"bedd34d7-ed16-23e0-5fbc-2e8010aed255","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"1a02a62e-88d9-ae49-a40c-852dae54710c","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your blog posts process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-20],"id":"2004f99e-4f71-46c4-4212-20c7db9884c1","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Required Fields Present?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Required Fields Present?":{"main":[[{"node":"Frame the Assignment","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Abort — Malformed Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Frame the Assignment":{"main":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Google Gemini Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Research Specialist (Sub-workflow)":{"ai_tool":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_tool","index":0}]]},"Draft Specialist (Sub-workflow)":{"ai_tool":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_tool","index":0}]]},"Review Specialist (Sub-workflow)":{"ai_tool":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_tool","index":0}]]},"Enforce Result Schema":{"ai_outputParser":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_outputParser","index":0}]]},"Coordinator Agent":{"main":[[{"node":"Unpack Sections","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Unpack Sections":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Deliverable to Airtable","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Deliverable to Airtable":{"main":[[{"node":"Load Previous Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Load Previous Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Drift vs Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Drift vs Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Serialize Run Output (CSV)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Serialize Run Output (CSV)":{"main":[[{"node":"Archive Row Snapshot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Archive Row Snapshot":{"main":[[{"node":"Enrich with Reference Data","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Enrich with Reference Data":{"main":[[{"node":"Fold In Enrichment Fields","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fold In Enrichment Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Completion Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Completion Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Run Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Run Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Fingerprint for Idempotency","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fingerprint for Idempotency":{"main":[[{"node":"Drop Already-Processed Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Drop Already-Processed Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Offload to Post-Process Sub-workflow":{"main":[[{"node":"Record Sub-workflow Result","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Sub-workflow Result":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Drafts Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Drafts Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Notion)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Notion)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Escalate Failure to Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Park in Dead-Letter Queue","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"3e2d2a4c-e6ce-4e03-b0c2-fb37a3297dfa","id":"FDX05365"}